data.description: Custom built basement home with tons of character on 1/2 acre cul-de-sac lot.  Very sought after subdivision with no hoa.  5 Beds 3 baths with a huge bonus room in the downstairs basement.  Split floorplan layout with 3 bedrooms upstairs and 2 downstairs. Living room, family room, separate formal dining area, and vaulted ceilings make this the perfect place to call home. Backyard has mature landscaping with area big enough for a pool. 2 RV gates and a sports court also makes this the perfect unique property for the right buyer that is looking for a custom property. Very peaceful location with mountain views in the distance, close to shopping, dining, schools, and the freeways just a skip away.
